teaser_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F5f%2FTomb_Raider_official_teaser_poster.jpg&h=6b1a7b34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.小說家愛德華&middot;摩拉（Edward &quot;Eddie&quot; Morra，布萊德利&middot;古柏飾）江郎才盡，不事生產的他，已然坐吃山空，面臨出版社的壓力，女友琳蒂（Lindy，艾比&middot;寇尼許飾）也離他而去。<br />\n愛德華與女友分手後，巧遇前妻的兄弟維農&middot;甘特（Vernon Gant，強尼&middot;威特沃斯飾），並拿到一款能「變聰明」的藥物：「NZT」<br />\n<br />\n2.在蘿拉&middot;卡芙特的父親理查&middot;卡芙特失蹤後，蘿拉靠騎單車送外賣為生，在她出車禍並被帶到警局後，里查德在商業上的夥伴安娜保釋了她，並警告她若不繼承里查德的遺產，那些財產可能會被賣掉。在蘿拉不情願地接受後，她發現一則來自里查的訊息，得知他失蹤前正在調查邪馬台女王卑彌呼。里查要求蘿拉燒掉研究，但蘿拉沒有這麼做，反而踏上尋找父親的旅途<br />\n<br />\n3.<img src=\"https://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/films/2017/01/04/deadpool_trans_NvBQzQNjv4BqZgEkZX3M936N5BQK4Va8RWtT0gK_6EfZT336f62EI5U.jpg?imwidth=450\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Ffilms%2F2017%2F01%2F04%2Fdeadpool_trans_NvBQzQNjv4BqZgEkZX3M936N5BQK4Va8RWtT0gK_6EfZT336f62EI5U.jpg%3Fimwidth%3D450&h=fe27bb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=a8SR4HwKjiqR%2FARXhlfUgE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=b053bdc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=a8SR4HwKjiqR%2FARXhlfUgE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=066ac774\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /